{
  "video_id": "xGKiyfOeV6c",
  "title": "I Fell in Love When I Was 3",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 300.0,
      "end_time": 2460.0,
      "text": "It all started in my hometown."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2460.0,
      "end_time": 4540.0,
      "text": "We had a pretty big house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4540.0,
      "end_time": 7540.0,
      "text": "with about three floors all for ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7540.0,
      "end_time": 11000.0,
      "text": "My grandpa ran a school where\nmy grandma worked as a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11000.0,
      "end_time": 12760.0,
      "text": "so between school hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "they tutored kids at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14160.0,
      "end_time": 16540.0,
      "text": "It was only 10 children at the very beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16540.0,
      "end_time": 19240.0,
      "text": "but it quickly grew to over 150."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19240.0,
      "end_time": 21620.0,
      "text": "I was just three years old at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21620.0,
      "end_time": 23740.0,
      "text": "so instead of learning\nlike all the other older kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23740.0,
      "end_time": 25740.0,
      "text": "I just stared at them through the windows."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 27620.0,
      "text": "Then, one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27620.0,
      "end_time": 28880.0,
      "text": "I saw him."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28880.0,
      "end_time": 30440.0,
      "text": "A new student."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30440.0,
      "end_time": 33540.0,
      "text": "His name was Jonas."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 36300.0,
      "text": "We were close enough in age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36300.0,
      "end_time": 38400.0,
      "text": "that we eventually started talking to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 38400.0,
      "end_time": 40300.0,
      "text": "We were just classmates at the start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 40300.0,
      "end_time": 42700.0,
      "text": "but soon we became really close."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 42700.0,
      "end_time": 45680.0,
      "text": "He used to stay back even after all his friends left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 45680.0,
      "end_time": 47300.0,
      "text": "just to play with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 47480.0,
      "end_time": 49500.0,
      "text": "He was fun, sweet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 49500.0,
      "end_time": 52360.0,
      "text": "but most of all he was really kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 54940.0,
      "text": "I don’t remember much since I was so young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 54940.0,
      "end_time": 57160.0,
      "text": "but I remember he was my best friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 57400.0,
      "end_time": 58920.0,
      "text": "But then, one night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 58920.0,
      "end_time": 62420.0,
      "text": "my mom sat me down and told me\nsomething that would change all of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 62420.0,
      "end_time": 64480.0,
      "text": "We were moving to another country."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 64680.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67460.0,
      "text": "I was too small to understand\nwhy we were moving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 67460.0,
      "end_time": 69840.0,
      "text": "but I knew I was about to lose my best friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 71600.0,
      "end_time": 72780.0,
      "text": "The good thing was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 72780.0,
      "end_time": 74340.0,
      "text": "every summer vacation"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 74340.0,
      "end_time": 76340.0,
      "text": "we’d be back to visit my grandparents."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 76600.0,
      "end_time": 78340.0,
      "text": "So, with luck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 78340.0,
      "end_time": 81140.0,
      "text": "I’d be able to see him at least once a year too."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 81320.0,
      "end_time": 85100.0,
      "text": "This was how we caught up every\nyear until I reached fifth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 85100.0,
      "end_time": 87700.0,
      "text": "and our family faced some\nmoney problems, and we just"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 87700.0,
      "end_time": 89940.0,
      "text": "couldn’t make it to visit my grandparents."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 89940.0,
      "end_time": 91940.0,
      "text": "There was no way for him to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 91940.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "I wouldn’t be back this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 97180.0,
      "text": "and I became scared that he would think\nI abandoned him and forget about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 97180.0,
      "end_time": 100420.0,
      "text": "But eventually, it was\nme who forgot about him."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 100420.0,
      "end_time": 103000.0,
      "text": "It had been three years since our last vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 106200.0,
      "text": "and I was distracted by the new\nlife and people that I had found."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "Finally, when I was in 8th,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 111300.0,
      "text": "we went to meet my grandparents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 111300.0,
      "end_time": 112800.0,
      "text": "and I was so happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112800.0,
      "end_time": 115600.0,
      "text": "I changed a lot and\nbecame a more social person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115600.0,
      "end_time": 118240.0,
      "text": "so I easily interacted with the kids of my age."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 118380.0,
      "end_time": 121680.0,
      "text": "A few minutes later, I saw\na guy who looked familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 121680.0,
      "end_time": 123560.0,
      "text": "I asked one of my friends who he was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123560.0,
      "end_time": 126160.0,
      "text": "and she replied, \"oh that’s Jonas."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 127080.0,
      "text": "Isn't he cute?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 127080.0,
      "end_time": 129880.0,
      "text": "Girls in our school are head over heels for him.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 129880.0,
      "end_time": 132860.0,
      "text": "Honestly, I stopped listening\nafter she said the name “Jonas”,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132860.0,
      "end_time": 135680.0,
      "text": "because all these memories\nsuddenly came flooding back."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 135680.0,
      "end_time": 137000.0,
      "text": "I was shocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 137000.0,
      "end_time": 139860.0,
      "text": "And, I remembered that he was the one."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 139860.0,
      "end_time": 141740.0,
      "text": "The one that I forgot."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141740.0,
      "end_time": 144900.0,
      "text": "And, the flash of memories turned to guilt."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146720.0,
      "end_time": 150560.0,
      "text": "After that day, I kept dreaming\nabout him, day and night."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 150940.0,
      "end_time": 154040.0,
      "text": "All I wanted for the moment was to see him."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 154420.0,
      "end_time": 157020.0,
      "text": "The next year, when I came back for my vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 157020.0,
      "end_time": 158280.0,
      "text": "there he was."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 158280.0,
      "end_time": 161300.0,
      "text": "He hadn't changed one bit except he was taller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 161300.0,
      "end_time": 163800.0,
      "text": "and this time, he had love in his eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164220.0,
      "end_time": 166540.0,
      "text": "We talked for hours and hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 166540.0,
      "end_time": 168840.0,
      "text": "sharing stories with each other about our lives apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 168980.0,
      "end_time": 170920.0,
      "text": "Time flew by so quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 170920.0,
      "end_time": 173300.0,
      "text": "and with two days left before\nI would leave Jonas again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173300.0,
      "end_time": 175140.0,
      "text": "I decided I would confess."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175340.0,
      "end_time": 177280.0,
      "text": "So, the very next day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177280.0,
      "end_time": 179140.0,
      "text": "I sat him down and told him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 179140.0,
      "end_time": 181220.0,
      "text": "“I know we’ve fallen distant, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 181220.0,
      "end_time": 183220.0,
      "text": "I don’t know if you feel the same way, but…"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 183220.0,
      "end_time": 184520.0,
      "text": "…I love you”"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184520.0,
      "end_time": 186480.0,
      "text": "and then ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 188760.0,
      "end_time": 189880.0,
      "text": "The next day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 189880.0,
      "end_time": 192920.0,
      "text": "I was watching tutoring\nsessions, when I saw Jonas."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 192920.0,
      "end_time": 195180.0,
      "text": "But, he didn't even look at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 195440.0,
      "end_time": 197180.0,
      "text": "I was heartbroken and thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 197180.0,
      "end_time": 199420.0,
      "text": "maybe I was too forward with my feelings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 199720.0,
      "end_time": 202480.0,
      "text": "maybe he had lost interest\nafter all those years apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 202780.0,
      "end_time": 205300.0,
      "text": "Suddenly, I heard his voice from behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 205300.0,
      "end_time": 209040.0,
      "text": "and he told me he had been waiting for\nthe day when he’d finally be able to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 209320.0,
      "end_time": 210740.0,
      "text": "“I love you too”,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 211400.0,
      "end_time": 214000.0,
      "text": "and my heart nearly jumped out of my chest."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 214000.0,
      "end_time": 215820.0,
      "text": "I didn’t know what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 216520.0,
      "end_time": 218860.0,
      "text": "I skipped away, nearly falling over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218860.0,
      "end_time": 221040.0,
      "text": "half laughing and half crying."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 221720.0,
      "end_time": 224080.0,
      "text": "I could have stayed in that moment forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227160.0,
      "end_time": 229340.0,
      "text": "But, then I had to leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 229340.0,
      "end_time": 231660.0,
      "text": "So, we said our goodbyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 231660.0,
      "end_time": 233820.0,
      "text": "shared a hug that was long overdue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 233820.0,
      "end_time": 236220.0,
      "text": "and promised that we’d wait for each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 236620.0,
      "end_time": 237880.0,
      "text": "The following year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 237880.0,
      "end_time": 242900.0,
      "text": "every day that passed felt slower and\nslower, as I missed him more and more."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 242900.0,
      "end_time": 245480.0,
      "text": "I counted down the days until our vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 245480.0,
      "end_time": 247740.0,
      "text": "or really, until I could see him again."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 247740.0,
      "end_time": 249300.0,
      "text": "And when the day finally came,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 249300.0,
      "end_time": 250960.0,
      "text": "he came rushing to meet me."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250960.0,
      "end_time": 253080.0,
      "text": "I couldn’t hold my tears when I hugged him."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 253080.0,
      "end_time": 256320.0,
      "text": "When I pulled back to see his face\nproperly for the first time in a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 256320.0,
      "end_time": 259440.0,
      "text": "he leaned in and kissed me\non the cheek, and I froze."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 260060.0,
      "end_time": 262160.0,
      "text": "My heart was beating so fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262160.0,
      "end_time": 264520.0,
      "text": "There were a thousand butterflies in my stomach."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 267340.0,
      "end_time": 269380.0,
      "text": "After spending many days together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 269380.0,
      "end_time": 271380.0,
      "text": "the day came when I had to leave again."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 271380.0,
      "end_time": 275280.0,
      "text": "It had been almost exactly a year\nsince he said the words “I love you”,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 278920.0,
      "text": "and although it didn’t feel like\nwe had spent any time apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 278920.0,
      "end_time": 280560.0,
      "text": "I wasn’t ready to leave him."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 280560.0,
      "end_time": 283360.0,
      "text": "The night before my flight, sitting near a pond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 283360.0,
      "end_time": 285600.0,
      "text": "we talked about the\nnext time we’d see each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 285600.0,
      "end_time": 287360.0,
      "text": "maybe in a year, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 287360.0,
      "end_time": 288860.0,
      "text": "maybe a lot later."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 288860.0,
      "end_time": 291720.0,
      "text": "My eyes swelled, and jokingly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 291720.0,
      "end_time": 293840.0,
      "text": "“maybe you could come visit me.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 293840.0,
      "end_time": 294920.0,
      "text": "And before I knew it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 294920.0,
      "end_time": 298740.0,
      "text": "he held my face in his hands, and\ngently pressed his lips against mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 298740.0,
      "end_time": 299640.0,
      "text": "And that was it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 299640.0,
      "end_time": 302300.0,
      "text": "my very first kiss with my first love."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 302300.0,
      "end_time": 306180.0,
      "text": "It was the happiest and saddest night of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 308120.0,
      "end_time": 310340.0,
      "text": "And that’s what keeps me positive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 310340.0,
      "end_time": 313520.0,
      "text": "despite my family’s problems\nand symptoms of depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 313520.0,
      "end_time": 317300.0,
      "text": "knowing that he’s there for me\ndespite being a thousand miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 317300.0,
      "end_time": 319800.0,
      "text": "is what helps me get through all the hard times."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 319800.0,
      "end_time": 321480.0,
      "text": "I’m one of the lucky ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 321480.0,
      "end_time": 323300.0,
      "text": "whose first love has worked out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 323300.0,
      "end_time": 326220.0,
      "text": "but it doesn’t have to be a\nboy, just having someone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 326220.0,
      "end_time": 328880.0,
      "text": "something you love to hold onto"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 328880.0,
      "end_time": 330160.0,
      "text": "is what’s important."
    }
  ]
}